{"parentUuid":"98398c42-f102-4f5a-aa99-15e42bb415a1","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"dcbe4efb-6e32-4db6-a75a-aa49b911d737","agentId":"a51a7a37c07b9faa2","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01XrwkK6BDqgL5vHLqQ6pECA","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"AlphaEvolve DeepMind 0.7% datacenter compute Borg scheduling heuristic production\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Google DeepMind debuts algorithm evolving agent, AlphaEvolve • The Register\",\"url\":\"https://www.theregister.com/2025/05/15/google_deepmind_debuts_algorithm_evolving/\"},{\"title\":\"AlphaEvolve: Google DeepMind's New AI System - The Visla Blog\",\"url\":\"https://www.visla.us/blog/news/alphaevolve-google-deepminds-new-ai-system/\"},{\"title\":\"AlphaEvolve: A Gemini-powered coding agent for designing advanced algorithms - Google DeepMind - Michael Bargury\",\"url\":\"https://www.mbgsec.com/archive/2025-07-20-alphaevolve-a-gemini-powered-coding-agent-for-designing-advanced-algorithms-google-deepmind/\"},{\"title\":\"AlphaEvolve: How AI-Driven Algorithm Discovery Is Rewriting Computing | by Greg Robison | Medium\",\"url\":\"https://gregrobison.medium.com/alphaevolve-how-ai-driven-algorithm-discovery-is-rewriting-computing-4f27c88d8b27\"},{\"title\":\"AlphaEvolve: A Gemini-powered coding agent for designing advanced algorithms — Google DeepMind\",\"url\":\"https://deepmind.google/blog/alphaevolve-a-gemini-powered-coding-agent-for-designing-advanced-algorithms/\"},{\"title\":\"Google DeepMind’s new AI system can evolve new algorithms\",\"url\":\"https://www.techbrew.com/stories/2025/05/27/google-deepmind-ai-system-new-algorithms\"},{\"title\":\"AlphaEvolve: What Google's Coding Agent Is and How It Will Change Our Daily Lives\",\"url\":\"https://pasqualepillitteri.it/en/news/2233/alphaevolve-google-coding-agent-daily-life\"},{\"title\":\"AlphaEvolve - by Grigory Sapunov - Gonzo ML - Substack\",\"url\":\"https://gonzoml.substack.com/p/alphaevolve\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what I found about AlphaEvolve and the DeepMind Borg scheduling heuristic:\n\nAlphaEvolve is an evolutionary coding agent powered by large language models for general-purpose algorithm discovery and optimization. It was unveiled by Google's AI shop DeepMind.\n\nRegarding the specific application to datacenter scheduling, AlphaEvolve discovered a simple yet remarkably effective heuristic to help Borg orchestrate Google's vast data centers more efficiently, and this solution, now in production for over a year, continuously recovers, on average, 0.7% of Google's worldwide compute resources.\n\nThe coding agent proposed a heuristic function for online compute job scheduling that outperformed one running in production. Unlike deep reinforcement learning results, this solution is simpler and more interpretable.\n\nBeyond the Borg scheduling optimization, AlphaEvolve also helped optimize matrix multiplication operations involved in the training of Google's Gemini model family by speeding up its Pallas kernel 23 percent, for a training time reduction of 1 percent.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"63531b93-023c-47b7-8426-12e099e3c73d","timestamp":"2026-06-21T07:35:00.992Z","toolUseResult":{"query":"AlphaEvolve DeepMind 0.7% datacenter compute Borg scheduling heuristic production","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01GuM78W7KCm2MfVAx3yZE3j","content":[{"title":"Google DeepMind debuts algorithm evolving agent, AlphaEvolve • The Register","url":"https://www.theregister.com/2025/05/15/google_deepmind_debuts_algorithm_evolving/"},{"title":"AlphaEvolve: Google DeepMind's New AI System - The Visla Blog","url":"https://www.visla.us/blog/news/alphaevolve-google-deepminds-new-ai-system/"},{"title":"AlphaEvolve: A Gemini-powered coding agent for designing advanced algorithms - Google DeepMind - Michael Bargury","url":"https://www.mbgsec.com/archive/2025-07-20-alphaevolve-a-gemini-powered-coding-agent-for-designing-advanced-algorithms-google-deepmind/"},{"title":"AlphaEvolve: How AI-Driven Algorithm Discovery Is Rewriting Computing | by Greg Robison | Medium","url":"https://gregrobison.medium.com/alphaevolve-how-ai-driven-algorithm-discovery-is-rewriting-computing-4f27c88d8b27"},{"title":"AlphaEvolve: A Gemini-powered coding agent for designing advanced algorithms — Google DeepMind","url":"https://deepmind.google/blog/alphaevolve-a-gemini-powered-coding-agent-for-designing-advanced-algorithms/"},{"title":"Google DeepMind’s new AI system can evolve new algorithms","url":"https://www.techbrew.com/stories/2025/05/27/google-deepmind-ai-system-new-algorithms"},{"title":"AlphaEvolve: What Google's Coding Agent Is and How It Will Change Our Daily Lives","url":"https://pasqualepillitteri.it/en/news/2233/alphaevolve-google-coding-agent-daily-life"},{"title":"AlphaEvolve - by Grigory Sapunov - Gonzo ML - Substack","url":"https://gonzoml.substack.com/p/alphaevolve"}]},"Based on the search results, here's what I found about AlphaEvolve and the DeepMind Borg scheduling heuristic:\n\nAlphaEvolve is an evolutionary coding agent powered by large language models for general-purpose algorithm discovery and optimization. It was unveiled by Google's AI shop DeepMind.\n\nRegarding the specific application to datacenter scheduling, AlphaEvolve discovered a simple yet remarkably effective heuristic to help Borg orchestrate Google's vast data centers more efficiently, and this solution, now in production for over a year, continuously recovers, on average, 0.7% of Google's worldwide compute resources.\n\nThe coding agent proposed a heuristic function for online compute job scheduling that outperformed one running in production. Unlike deep reinforcement learning results, this solution is simpler and more interpretable.\n\nBeyond the Borg scheduling optimization, AlphaEvolve also helped optimize matrix multiplication operations involved in the training of Google's Gemini model family by speeding up its Pallas kernel 23 percent, for a training time reduction of 1 percent."],"durationSeconds":6.884737124999985,"searchCount":1},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"98398c42-f102-4f5a-aa99-15e42bb415a1","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/gg/Work/Yogi","sessionId":"d8d6b712-ec33-4776-a194-d9a72216a25f","version":"2.1.183","gitBranch":"main","slug":"bright-wondering-lantern"}
